description:
Single-cell RNA-seq data of untreated (F43N, F43R) and DKK-1 inhibitor treated (OSW3, OSW4, OSW5, OSW6) patient derived xenografts (PDXs).&nbsp; 
 human_cells_scanpy_object.h5ad -- contains Scanpy analysis of human cells from untreated and DKK-1 inhibitor treated PDXs 
 raw_counts_cellranger_output.zip -- contains the raw expression counts of untreated and DKK-1 inhibitor treated PDXs cells outputted by CellRanger.&nbsp;

